query:
SELECT id, canonical_name
        FROM data.entities_place
        WHERE ST_DWithin(
            geo_center::geography,
            ST_SetSRID(ST_MakePoint($1, $2), 4326)::geography,
            75.0
        )
        ORDER BY ST_Distance(
            geo_center::geography,
            ST_SetSRID(ST_MakePoint($1, $2), 4326)::geography
        )
        LIMIT 1
